laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Reduced amniotic fluid was confirmed; umbilical artery PI increased from 1.23 to 1.27, while middle cerebral artery PI decreased from 1.62 to 1.21 and cerebroplacental ratio decreased from 1.32 to 0.95.

laboratory_examinations.findings: All tests resulted negative for amphetamines, benzodiazepines, cocaine, methadone, opiates, and cannabinoids.
